    public interface IBusMirrorChannelMappingFlexray
extends IEntity, IBusMirrorChannelMapping
    IBusMirrorChannelMappingFlexray: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This element defines the bus mirroring between a CAN, LIN or FlexRay sourceChannel and a FlexRay targetChannel.

      • getTransmissionDeadline

        double getTransmissionDeadline()
        Query the value of the attribute TransmissionDeadline.

        Time in seconds after which the collection of source frames into the destination frame is stopped and the frame is sent at the latest. If omitted, destination frames are only sent when full or when the time stamp overflows.

        Returns:
        The value or null
